74">签署了一封通向大逃生的公开信</a>，要求他们删除巴克莱作为赞助商。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="皮特·多尔蒂（Pete Doherty" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/oSjOLr92kL8?start=166&enablejsapi=1#038;feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>该节日自2006年以来一直举行，以前的表演者包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/charli-xcx">Charli XCX</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sam-fender">Sam Fender</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/fontaines-d-c">Fontaines DC</a> 。</p><p>帖子<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-great-escape-2025-add-120-names-to-line-up-plus-spotlight-show-with-pete-doherty-and-warmduscher-3834703">The Great Escape 2025在阵容中添加了120个名字，以及Pete Doherty和Warmduscher的Spotlight Show，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
