5年的《邮报》 2025年的第二波艺术家阵容</a>。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/The-Futureheads-The-Slow-Readers-Club-and-The-Subways.-Credit-Samir-Hussein-Shirlaine-Forrest-and-Marc-Marnie.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="未来的头脑，缓慢的读者俱乐部和地铁。信用Samir Hussein，Shirlaine Forrest和Marc Marnie通过Getty" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/The-Futureheads-The-Slow-Readers-Club-and-The-Subways.-Credit-Samir-Hussein-Shirlaine-Forrest-and-Marc-Marnie.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/The-Futureheads-The-Slow-Readers-Club-and-The-Subways.-Credit-Samir-Hussein-Shirlaine-Forrest-and-Marc-Marnie-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/The-Futureheads-The-Slow-Readers-Club-and-The-Subways.-Credit-Samir-Hussein-Shirlaine-Forrest-and-Marc-Marnie-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/The-Futureheads-The-Slow-Readers-Club-and-The-Subways.-Credit-Samir-Hussein-Shirlaine-Forrest-and-Marc-Marnie-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/The-Futureheads-The-Slow-Readers-Club-and-The-Subways.-Credit-Samir-Hussein-Shirlaine-Forrest-and-Marc-Marnie-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/The-Futureheads-The-Slow-Readers-Club-and-The-Subways.-Credit-Samir-Hussein-Shirlaine-Forrest-and-Marc-Marnie-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-futureheads">未来的头脑</a>，缓慢的读者俱乐部，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-subways">地铁</a>等人已被宣布，这是<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/y-not-festival">Y非节日</a>2025年第二浪行为的一部分。</p><p>一年一度的音乐狂欢节将于7月31日至8月3日返回其德比郡派克豪尔的家。今年是音乐节18周年纪念日。您可以访问<a href="https://ynotfestival.com/tickets/">此处</a>购买节日的门票。</p><p>作为在音乐狂欢中演出的第二波行为的一部分宣布的其他行为包括威尔金森，Fish56octagon，Switch Presents，Academic，Fickle Friends，The Lilacs，Callum Beattie，Callum Beattie，Arxx，Arxx，10月Drift，Northside，Northside，Crystal Tides，Crystal tide，Crystal tide，Crystal tide，Crystal tide，Crystal tide，Crystal tides， Harpy，喜马拉雅山，Mercians，果园，铺路，廉价的刺激，骗子，Lunabay，Ariel Salad，湾板，由猫头鹰，Aiko，Skies，Skies和Small Fortunes Paradise Circus抚养长大。 </p><figure id="attachment_3834724" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3834724" style="width: 1600px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3834724" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Y-Not-Second-Line-up-Poster.-Credit-PRESS.jpg" alt="y不是第二排海报。信用：出版" width="1600" height="2842" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Y-Not-Second-Line-up-Poster.-Credit-PRESS.jpg 1600w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Y-Not-Second-Line-up-Poster.-Credit-PRESS-400x711.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Y-Not-Second-Line-up-Poster.-Credit-PRESS-800x1421.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Y-Not-Second-Line-up-Poster.-Credit-PRESS-696x1236.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Y-Not-Second-Line-up-Poster.-Credit-PRESS-1392x2473.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Y-Not-Second-Line-up-Poster.-Credit-PRESS-1068x1897.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3834724" class="wp-caption-text"> y不是第二排海报。信用：出版</figcaption></figure><p>Y Not Festival的节日经理内森·哈里森（Nathan Harrison）在新闻稿中谈到了该法案的新成员时说：“我们很高兴能回到我们的第18版《 Y》（Y Not），这是如此令人难以置信的阵容。未来的头脑，缓慢的读者俱乐部和地铁是已经堆叠的法案的绝佳补充，与我们的头条新闻旁边的神童，Courteeners，Madness和The Wombats一起。</p><p> “Y Not has always been about bringing the best live music to Derbyshire, and this year is no exception. From massive crowd-pleasers to exciting emerging talent and some huge late night DJs, we can&#39;t wait to welcome everyone back for another unforgettable weekend.”</p><p> The new acts follow the <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/y-not-2025-the-prodigy-courteeners-madness-the-wombats-top-line-up-3816122">previously announced first acts including headliners</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-prodigy">The Prodigy</a> , <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/courteeners">Courteeners</a> , <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/madness">Madness</a> and <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-wombats">The Wombats</a> .</p><p> Elsewhere on the line-up are <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/primal-scream">Primal Scream</a> , <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-last-dinner-party">The Last Dinner Party</a> , <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/franz-ferdinand">Franz Ferdinand</a> , <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sigrid">Sigrid</a> , <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/shed-seven">Shed Seven</a> , <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/hard-life">hard life</a> , <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/annie-mac">Annie Mac</a> , <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-ks">The K&#39;s</a> , <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/maximo-park">Maximo Park</a> , <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-pigeon-detectives">The Pigeon Detectives</a> , <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/professor-green">Professor Green</a> , <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-hunna">The Hunna</a> , Red Rum Club and more 。</p><p> Last year&#39;s edition saw the likes of <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jamie-t">Jamie T</a> , <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/noel-gallaghers-high-flying-birds">Noel Gallagher&#39;s High Flying Birds</a> and <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kaiser-chiefs">Kaiser Chiefs</a> take to the stage.</p><p> The post <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/y-not-festival-2025-announce-second-wave-of-artists-for-line-up-3834711">Y Not Festival 2025 announce second wave of artists for line-up</a> appeared first on <a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
